name: Chronomaly Tuspa Rocket
desc:
If this card is Normal/Special Summoned: You can send 1 "Chronomaly" monster from your Main Deck or Extra Deck to the GY, then target 1 face-up monster on the field; until the end of the turn, that monster loses 200 ATK for every Level or Rank of the sent monster. If this card is used as material for the Xyz Summon of a "Number" monster, that monster gains the following effect. You can only use each effect of "Chronomaly Tuspa Rocket" once per turn.
